<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="peace-n">peace <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /piːs/    美 /piːs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[可用单数] 和平：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>peace talks</strong> 
和平会谈</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The people of the world love peace. 
世界人民热爱和平。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>平静；安宁</strong></h4>
<p>the state of being calm：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Keeping on doing good deeds brings us <strong>peace of mind</strong>.
坚持做好事会给我们带来内心的平静。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>安静；清静</strong></h4>
<p>the state of being quiet：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The father wanted to be left alone to enjoy some <strong>peace and quiet</strong>. 
那位父亲想一个人享受一下清静。</p><footer>2012 上海</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-peace">at peace</h3>
<p>1.<strong>处于和平 / 平静状态：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The countries have been at peace for more than a century. 
这些国家和平共处已有一个多世纪了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her mind is at peace. 
她心境平和。</p></div>

<h3 id="in-peace">in peace</h3>
<p>1.<strong>和平地；安宁地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The two communities live together in peace. 
这两个社区相安无事。</p></div>

<h3 id="make-ones-peace-with">make (one’s) peace with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>同…言归于好：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They finally made peace with each other after two weeks of arguing. 
争吵了两周后，他们终于和好了。</p></div></div>